{"tid":2376343,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳彥霖逝世 16 個月　王婆婆尚十舉標語被捕　警指阻差辦公　仍被扣留","createTime":"2021-01-22T17:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T02:10:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5029910d32028ef532a2f3bdadc0d89cf1e1411d","tid":2376343,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T17:09:02.000Z","msg":"1 月 22 日是陳彥霖逝世 1 年 4 個月，有市民在將軍澳尚德十字路口自發默哀。示威常客「王婆婆」王鳳瑤在場高舉標語，被警方指阻礙行人過路上前勸止。警方指，由於她拒絕合作，警員遂以涉嫌「阻礙警務人員執行職務」作拘捕，被捕女子正被扣留。<br />\n<br />\n警方指晩上約七時，人員巡邏期間，發現一女子在將軍澳唐明街一行人過路處高舉標語，阻礙行人過路。人員上前勸止，但她拒絕合作。人員遂以涉嫌「阻礙警務人員執行職務」拘捕該名六十四歲姓王本地女子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%99%B3%E5%BD%A5%E9%9C%96%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-16-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E7%8E%8B%E5%A9%86%E5%A9%86%E5%B0%9A%E5%8D%81%E8%88%89%E6%A8%99%E8%AA%9E%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8C%87%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E9%259C%2596%25E9%2580%259D%25E4%25B8%2596-16-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%25A9%2586%25E5%25A9%2586%25E5%25B0%259A%25E5%258D%2581%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%25A8%2599%25E8%25AA%259E%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%2F&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5PsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=93066f47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E9%259C%2596%25E9%2580%259D%25E4%25B8%2596-16-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%25A9%2586%25E5%25A9%2586%25E5%25B0%259A%25E5%258D%2581%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%25A8%2599%25E8%25AA%259E%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%2F&h=a8147a78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%99%B3%E5%BD%A5%E9%9C%96%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-16-%E5%80%8B%E6%9